Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:26.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:39.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:45.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
